Controls
Driving Mode:
WASD/Arrows - Drive
Space - Handbrake
Ctrl - Boost
Shift - Off-road mode
C - Camera view
F - Toggle walk mode
6 - Toggle drone mode
Walking Mode:
Arrows - Move
WASD - Look around
Space - Jump
Shift - Run (2x speed)
Right Click + Drag - Mouse look
C - Camera view
F - Toggle drive mode
6 - Toggle drone mode
Drone Mode:
WASD - Move forward/back/strafe
Arrows - Look around
Mouse - Look around
Space - Fly up
Ctrl/Shift - Fly down
6 - Exit drone mode

General:
N - Next city (teleport)
R - Record/stop track
M - Toggle map
Esc - Pause
